text: I actually made most of this track back in 2009. I've taken a healthy break from remixing/composing music after 3 years of intense hours playing around FL Studio. I'll probably get back to it in the near future. Trying out different genres is what motivates me, though I often end up making upbeat music. This is one of the more techno-y﻿ tracks I've made.
